### 5. No Financial Transactions
- Our App does not process any payments, banking transactions, or cryptocurrency operations.

### 6. Termination
- We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your account if you violate these terms.

### 7. Disclaimer
- We provide the App on an "as is" basis without warranties of any kind.
- We are not responsible for any damages resulting from App usage.

## Privacy Policy

### 1. Data Collection
- We collect only necessary data required for account registration (e.g., email, username).
